00:25:40,635 --> 00:25:45,937
[SPEAKER_11]: She's very familiar with the Article 97 process, too.

258
00:25:47,018 --> 00:25:53,020
[SPEAKER_11]: Yes, so open space is protected in the Commonwealth, but it requires legislative action to

259
00:25:53,820 --> 00:25:59,624
