262
00:26:05,767 --> 00:26:13,872
[SPEAKER_10]: But land swap is also a trigger to comply with the state regulations for the META regulations.

263
00:26:13,952 --> 00:26:18,075
[SPEAKER_10]: And so there's additional soft costs associated with completing land swap.

264
00:26:20,016 --> 00:26:20,336
[SPEAKER_10]: I think

265
00:26:21,104 --> 00:26:27,027
