268
00:26:37,951 --> 00:26:39,312
[SPEAKER_10]: That is a question we have as well.

269
00:26:41,233 --> 00:26:49,917
[SPEAKER_02]: So the other salient points are that the mayor, the superintendent, and I spoke with the state delegation, all four of them.

