278
00:27:45,709 --> 00:27:47,009
[SPEAKER_02]: They've been wonderfully cooperative.

279
00:27:47,725 --> 00:27:49,766
[SPEAKER_02]: and supportive as has DCR.

280
00:27:50,687 --> 00:28:01,152
[SPEAKER_02]: So there are potentially paths forward there, but we don't know that for sure one way or the other at this point.

281
00:28:01,392 --> 00:28:05,595
