00:31:37,335 --> 00:31:47,060
[SPEAKER_06]: the first two phases so that the school could remain in operation while construction activity takes place behind the school and on the side of the school.

319
00:31:47,080 --> 00:32:06,770
[SPEAKER_06]: So you can see on the image on the right, we've started to take all the things that we really liked about this scheme, all the adjacencies that we learned about in the previous study, all the need for access for some of the CTE spaces that need ground floor yards and things like that.

320
00:32:07,617 --> 00:32:13,179
[SPEAKER_06]: and started to manipulate it to be within the deep construction zone.

321
00:32:13,219 --> 00:32:17,601
[SPEAKER_06]: So that's why you see this pretty hard edge on the Western and Northern side of the site.

