00:56:19,566 --> 00:56:22,907
[SPEAKER_02]: So yes, we can certainly make these choices.

565
00:56:23,067 --> 00:56:32,691
[SPEAKER_02]: And if we get, we have a path forward that allows us to sort of shift that deed restriction or lift it in exchange for something.

