[SPEAKER_06]: I'll quote for you, advisory number 45.

670
01:04:33,911 --> 01:04:40,798
[SPEAKER_06]: At the preliminary design program phase, all site for the lease should be presented with potential development restrictions identified.

671
01:04:41,319 --> 01:04:48,326
