672
01:04:49,127 --> 01:04:52,250
[SPEAKER_06]: So obviously we didn't comply with that and it's a problem because the MSBA

673
01:04:56,708 --> 01:05:03,353
[SPEAKER_06]: the enabling statute, regulation, as well as the advisory guidelines, pose risk of losing support of the project.

674
01:05:03,513 --> 01:05:07,716
