708
01:07:59,818 --> 01:08:00,399
[SPEAKER_06]: Right, right.

709
01:08:00,459 --> 01:08:06,764
[SPEAKER_06]: Like a trailer 24 by 36, it's about 900 square foot, maybe 960.

710
01:08:07,124 --> 01:08:10,527
[SPEAKER_06]: Let's call it 1,000 just for ease of moving around.

