[SPEAKER_06]: In option A, where would those modulars go?

713
01:08:23,072 --> 01:08:31,615
[SPEAKER_06]: we go way back, we literally looked at a couple different locations on the site where you could just physically place them before you get to any of the considerations of where would you want to place them.

