[SPEAKER_06]: So there's a limited number of areas.

715
01:08:34,416 --> 01:08:45,399
[SPEAKER_06]: And I think we were looking exclusively at a two-story modular situation because of all the various competing site interests on a very packed site, the fact that we still have to educate students here while construction is ongoing.

716
01:08:45,419 --> 01:08:46,280
[SPEAKER_06]: So that drove us.

717
01:08:46,800 --> 01:08:52,862
[SPEAKER_06]: I would say the most viable site, again, ignoring all other considerations, is on the parking lot to the south

718
01:08:53,566 --> 01:09:00,588
