719
01:09:00,668 --> 01:09:04,749
[SPEAKER_06]: It does take away the most viable parking area on the overall site.

720
01:09:05,589 --> 01:09:15,891
[SPEAKER_06]: As a downside to this, there are some other options as well, but it's not completely blue sky in terms of where we can position it.

