01:09:15,911 --> 01:09:18,832
[SPEAKER_06]: That option works with the neighbors at the moment, right?

722
01:09:21,382 --> 01:09:32,112
[SPEAKER_06]: Sorry, the well so I'm picking up on another school committee member talked about, can we actually, you know, use The protected spaces lay down space.

