01:09:50,846 --> 01:09:52,628
[SPEAKER_06]: I mean, they are temporary buildings by nature.

728
01:09:52,668 --> 01:09:54,289
[SPEAKER_06]: They're not something permanent that's getting there.

729
01:09:54,549 --> 01:10:07,997
[SPEAKER_06]: We haven't gone through that exact situation in our experience, but I could see it actually going one or two ways pretty easily in terms of how the discussion played out because they are temporary as opposed to permanent structures.

730
01:10:09,118 --> 01:10:13,941
[SPEAKER_06]: And so let's go with the idea that they're on the parking lot to the south there.

731
01:10:17,223 --> 01:10:18,084
[SPEAKER_06]: Have you all thought about

