[SPEAKER_02]: I don't think it will happen in June because we're still talking about many options.

790
01:14:57,448 --> 01:15:08,013
[SPEAKER_02]: So there would be like many lives to talk about, but as soon as there is a single option, I think that becomes like much easier to plan for and manage, and we can definitely dedicate a meeting to that.

