[SPEAKER_06]: We have started those conversations with the athletic director.

797
01:15:37,903 --> 01:15:42,126
[SPEAKER_06]: and the district offices as well to try to figure out what opportunities are there.

798
01:15:42,146 --> 01:15:51,252
