01:38:37,569 --> 01:38:48,555
[SPEAKER_06]: So they, and we asked, we asked that question, you know, about the community spaces and yeah, they said they won't tell us what we can and can't build.

1070
01:38:48,915 --> 01:38:56,659
[SPEAKER_06]: They just want to be, they just want to make sure that we have looked at, you know, several different options.

1071
01:38:56,699 --> 01:38:58,320
